  "action_title": "Plant turf",
  "key_messages": "Key Messages:\n\nTwo randomized, controlled studies in the UK\u00a0found that planting turf from intact heathland sites increased the abundance or cover of heathland species. One of these studies\u00a0also found that planting turf increased the seedling abundance for a majority of heathland plant species.\nOne randomized, controlled study in the UK\u00a0found that planting turf increased forb cover, and reduced grass cover.\nOne randomized, replicated, controlled study in Iceland\u00a0found that planting large turves from intact heathland sites increased the number of plant species, but smaller turves did not."
